description: [``botocore``] Bedrock AgentCore release for Runtime, and Memory.
[``botocore``] Bedrock AgentCore release for Gateway, and Memory including Self-Managed Strategies support for Memory.
[``botocore``] Added new viewer security policy, TLSv1.2_2025, for CloudFront.
[``botocore``] Addition of AuditContext in GetTable/GetTables Request
[``botocore``] Add InvokedViaFunctionUrl context key to limit invocations to only FURL invokes.
[``botocore``] This release adds APIs that allow you to specify CIDR ranges in your ODB peering connection.
[``botocore``] Updated the text in the Important section of the ModifyDBClusterParameterGroup page.
